# Implementation Plan - Hello World Lightning App

This plan outlines the steps to initialize a new React Native application and integrate the Breez SDK to create a simple "Hello World" Lightning Network wallet.

## Goal Description
Create a functional React Native app named `BoltZap` (Project Name: `BoltZap`) that:
1.  Initializes **LDK Node** (Self-custodial Lightning Node).
2.  Generates a dedicated Lightning Node ID.
3.  Can receive a small testnet payment.

